%5B%7B%22title%22%3A%22Art%20Basel%20gives%20Miami%20another%20excuse%20to%20party%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221440%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20split%20image%20shows%20a%20woman%20posing%20by%20a%20pink%20and%20purple%20mural%20of%20a%20face%20in%20Miami%20(left)%20and%20an%20Earth-like%20structure%20in%20a%20gallery%20(right).%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F657cbf860ec98e92f7502fa9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EBusiness%20Insider's%20Chlo%C3%A9%20Pantazi-Wolber%20(left)%20visited%20Miami%20Beach%20Art%20Basel%20found%20a%20weeklong%2C%20citywide%20party.%3Cp%3EChlo%C3%A9%20Pantazi-Wolber%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EI%20visited%20Art%20Basel%20Miami%20Beach%20as%20it%20turned%2021%20this%20year.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20world-famous%20fair%20is%20as%20much%20about%20being%20seen%20as%20it%20is%20seeing%20the%20art.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EWhat%20started%20as%20an%20event%20for%20galleries%20and%20collectors%20has%20since%20become%20a%20week-long%2C%20citywide%20party.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20traffic%20is%20a%20nightmare.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20sitting%20in%20the%20back%20of%20an%20Uber%20on%20my%20way%20to%20dinner%20in%20Wynwood%2C%20anxiously%20refreshing%20Google%20Maps%20to%20monitor%20the%20traffic%20ahead.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20it's%20Thursday%20night%20during%20Miami%20Art%20Week%2C%20so%20what%20should%20be%20a%2020-minute%20drive%20from%20South%20Beach%20takes%20close%20to%20two%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20in%20town%20for%20my%20first%20Art%20Basel%2C%20even%20though%20at%20this%20point%20I%20haven't%20yet%20seen%20a%20piece%20of%20art%20besides%20a%20print%20in%20my%20hotel%20lobby.%20I%20learn%20quickly%20that%20the%20chaos%20isn't%20confined%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fmiami-beach-travel-guide-hotels-activities-restaurants-and-more-2021-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EMiami%20Beach%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20Convention%20Center%2C%20where%20the%20world-famous%20annual%20festival%20is%20being%20held%20from%20December%208-10.%20The%20whole%20city%20is%20in%20party%20mode.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELeading%20up%20to%20the%20fair%2C%20invites%20to%20events%20around%20Miami%20pour%20into%20my%20inbox%3A%20brunches%3B%20cocktail%20hours%3B%20celebrity%20apparel%20pop-ups%20at%20hotels%3B%20art%20installations%20at%20design%20houses%20like%20Fendi.%20It's%20not%20clear%20if%20these%20functions%20are%20all%20related%20to%20the%20actual%20art%20festival%2C%20but%20that%20doesn't%20seem%20to%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20first%20event%20is%20the%20opening%20party%20for%20The%20Art%20of%20Hip-Hop's%20permanent%20space%20at%20Wynwood's%20Museum%20of%20Graffiti%2C%20kicking%20off%20with%20its%20first%20exhibit%2C%20%26quot%3BFrom%20the%20Bronx%20to%20the%20Beach.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe're%20greeted%20by%20a%20wall%20of%20boomboxes%20%E2%80%94%20an%20instant%20photo%20op.%20Then%2C%20there's%20the%20exhibit%20itself%2C%20an%20ode%20to%20hip-hop%20through%20album%20art%2C%20photography%2C%20and%20fashion.%20Guests%20in%20sequin%20boots%2C%20cutout%20dresses%2C%20and%20sheer%20looks%20meander%20through%20the%20displays%2C%20pausing%20to%20admire%20portraits%20of%20artists%20from%20Drake%20to%20Pitbull%2C%20or%20Henry%20Chalfant's%20photos%20of%20graffiti-covered%20subway%20trains%20in%201970s%20New%20York%20City.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221440%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20split%20image%20shows%20a%20woman%20wearing%20a%20denim%20jacket%20in%20front%20of%20a%20wall%20of%20boomboxes%20(left)%20and%20a%20butterfly%20mural%20at%20Miami's%20Museum%20of%20Graffiti%20(right).%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F657caad950edbc52a864e79a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author%2C%20pictured%20at%20Miami's%20Museum%20of%20Graffiti.%3Cp%3EChlo%C3%A9%20Pantazi-Wolber%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ELater%20on%2C%20LA%20Clippers%20point%20guard%20John%20Wall%20and%20rapper%20Fat%20Joe%20appear%2C%20the%20latter%20of%20whom%20performs%20out%20back%20where%20guests%20dance%20in%20front%20of%20a%20butterfly%20mural.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENext%2C%20I%20go%20to%20Gramp's%2C%20a%20Wynwood%20bar%20known%20for%20its%20drag%20shows.%20As%20I%20sip%20on%20a%20Rosemary's%20Baby%20cocktail%2C%20the%20Miami-famous%20drag%20queen%20Karla%20Croqueta%20declares%20that%20tonight's%20show%20is%20dedicated%20to%20Art%20Basel.%20%26quot%3BThank%20you%2C%20Art%20Basel%2C%26quot%3B%20Croqueta%20says%2C%20with%20more%20than%20a%20hint%20of%20sarcasm%2C%20before%20introducing%20the%20next%20act%20who%20lights%20up%20the%20stage%20performing%20Nicki%20Minaj's%20%26quot%3BMoment%20for%20Life%26quot%3B%20in%20a%20purple%20and%20Barbie-pink%20catsuit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20realize%20I'm%20watching%20some%20of%20the%20best%20performance%20art%20in%20town.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EAt%2021%2C%20Art%20Basel%20lives%20to%20party%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20year's%20art%20fair%20marks%20its%2021st%20year%20in%20Miami%20Beach.%20The%20prestigious%20festival%20originated%20in%20Basel%2C%20Switzerland%2C%20in%201970%2C%20where%20it%20continues%20to%20be%20held%20each%20spring%2C%20and%20eventually%20expanded%20into%20the%20US%20market%20with%20Miami%20in%202002.%20The%20fair%20is%20also%20held%20annually%20in%20Hong%20Kong%20and%20Paris.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20what%20started%20as%20Miami's%20edition%20of%20the%20art%20fair%20%E2%80%94%20meant%20to%20bring%20together%20the%20art%20world's%20major%20players%20%E2%80%94%20has%20since%20become%20a%20week-long%2C%20citywide%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Sculptures%20and%20paintings%20in%20a%20gallery.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F657cb96d0ec98e92f75026d5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20display%20at%20Miami%20Beach%20Art%20Basel.%3Cp%3EChlo%C3%A9%20Pantazi-Wolber%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20worry%20I've%20come%20too%20late%2C%20arriving%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20the%20week%2C%20but%20am%20assured%20by%20a%20Miami%20resident%20that%20all%20the%20good%20parties%20are%20on%20Thursday%20and%20Friday.%20When%20I%20tell%20Miami%20locals%20I%20want%20to%20go%20to%20the%20convention%20center%2C%20they're%20confused%20%E2%80%94%20go%20once%20if%20you%20want%20to%2C%20they%20say%2C%20but%20it's%20not%20really%20the%20point%20anymore.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20seem%20to%20be%20right.%20As%20I%20brush%20shoulders%20with%20influencers%2C%20publicists%2C%20and%20business%20moguls%20at%20functions%20filled%20with%20cocktails%20and%20canapes%2C%20I%20wonder%20where%20the%20artists%20are.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20actual%20fair%20means%20business%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20finally%20get%20to%20the%20convention%20center%2C%20I'm%20swept%20up%20in%20its%20grandness.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInside%20the%20cavernous%20hall%2C%20people%20funnel%20through%20several%20entrances%20to%20the%20festival%20floor%20and%20linger%20around%20the%20various%20shops%20and%20attractions%20in%20the%20lobby.%20Before%20I%20enter%2C%20a%20display%20of%20Louis%20Vuitton%20purses%20designed%20with%20the%20architect%20Frank%20Gehry%2C%20catches%20my%20eye.%20A%20retail%20associate%20tells%20me%20casually%20the%20items%20range%20from%20%2411%2C400%20to%20%2436%2C500.%20Welcome%20to%20Art%20Basel.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20main%20floor%2C%20I'm%20surprised%20to%20see%20something%20I%20recognize%20almost%20immediately%3A%20a%20large%20flower%20sculpture%20covered%20in%20oversized%20dots%20%E2%80%94%20Yayoi%20Kusama's%202018%20piece%2C%20%26quot%3BFlowers%20That%20Speak%20All%20About%20My%20Heart%20Given%20to%20the%20Sky.%26quot%3B%20A%20couple%20poses%20for%20a%20photo%20in%20front%20of%20the%20piece%20with%20their%20toddler%2C%20who%20is%20fascinated%20by%20the%20sculpture.%20I%20spot%20a%20number%20of%20fairgoers%20with%20their%20kids%2C%20which%20I%20didn't%20expect%2C%20but%20there's%20certainly%20enough%20to%20keep%20them%20entertained%20with%20277%20galleries%20bursting%20with%20often%20colorful%20art.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20know%20it'll%20be%20impossible%20to%20see%20everything%2C%20so%20I%20plan%20to%20zigzag%20through%20the%20galleries%20like%20I%20would%20aisles%20at%20the%20grocery%20store%2C%20but%20that%20doesn't%20quite%20work.%20Inevitably%2C%20something%20catches%20my%20eye%20and%20I%20turn%20a%20corner%20and%20find%20myself%20lost%20in%20the%20maze%20that%20is%20Art%20Basel.%20Consulting%20my%20floor%20map%2C%20I%20circle%20the%20key%20galleries%20I'd%20read%20about%2C%20determined%20to%20at%20least%20see%20what%20the%20art%20world%20is%20talking%20about.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20piece%20stays%20with%20me%3A%20Seung-taek%20Lee's%20%26quot%3BEarth%20Play%2C%26quot%3B%20an%20imposing%2C%20partially%20deflated%20balloon%20painted%20to%20look%20like%20the%20world.%20The%20structure%20is%20impossible%20to%20miss%20and%20makes%20a%20statement%20about%20the%20fragility%20of%20our%20planet%20as%20it%20sits%20on%20the%20floor%2C%20patched%20with%20small%20bits%20of%20tape%20covering%20up%20punctures%20and%20dents.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20piece%20isn't%20perfect%20%E2%80%94%20and%20that's%20the%20point.%20I%20read%20on%20nearby%20placards%20that%20the%20Korean%20artist%20has%20spent%20years%20toting%20the%20piece%2C%20from%20the%201990s%2C%20around%20the%20world%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.canalprojects.org%2Fprograms%2Fthe-earth-performance-reenactment%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eperformances%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20some%20of%20the%20art%2C%20I%20search%20for%20meaning%20but%20soon%20give%20up.%20A%20beating%20drum%20hanging%20upside-down%20from%20the%20ceiling.%20An%20ASMR%2