%20and%20a%20Petition%20Dismissed%20in%208%20Seconds%3A%20Behind%20the%20Civil%20Judge's%20Letter%20to%20the%20CJI%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%E2%80%9CI%20have%20no%20will%20to%20live%20anymore.%20I%20have%20been%20rendered%20to%20a%20walking%20corpse%20in%20the%20last%20year%20and%20a%20half.%20There%20is%20no%20purpose%20in%20carrying%20this%20soulless%20and%20lifeless%20body%20around%20anymore.%20There%20is%20no%20purpose%20left%20in%20my%20life.%20Kindly%20permit%20me%20to%20end%20my%20life%20in%20a%20dignified%20way.%20Let%20my%20life%20be%3A%20dismissed.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EA%20woman%20civil%20judge%20(junior%20division)%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20has%20sent%20shockwaves%20in%20the%20judicial%20circles%20after%20she%20penned%20a%20disturbing%20open%20letter%20to%20the%20topmost%20judge%20in%20the%20country%20to%20allow%20her%20to%20take%20her%20own%20life.%20Her%20grievance%3A%20she%20alleges%20that%20she%20was%20sexually%20harassed%20by%20a%20district%20judge%20and%20his%20associates%3B%20despite%20her%20following%20the%20proper%20procedure%20and%20knocking%20on%20the%20doors%20of%20all%20the%20higher%20courts%2C%20she%20has%20not%20been%20able%20to%20secure%20justice%20for%20herself.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThe%20letter%2C%20written%20in%20%E2%80%9Cextreme%20pain%20and%20despair%2C%E2%80%9D%20is%20addressed%20to%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20D.Y.%20Chandrachud.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EAfter%20the%20letter%20was%20widely%20shared%20on%20social%20media%20on%20Friday%2C%20December%2015%2C%20CJI%20Chandrachud%20sought%20a%20status%20report%20from%20the%20administration%20of%20the%20Allahabad%20high%20court%20on%20the%20inquiry%20being%20conducted%20into%20allegations%20of%20sexual%20harassment%20raised%20by%20the%20woman%20judge.%20The%20CJI%20is%20yet%20to%20publicly%20respond%20to%20the%20matter%20or%20issue%20directions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ENo%20system%20of%20redressal%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9CI%20have%20been%20sexually%20harassed%20by%20one%20particular%20district%20judge%20and%20his%20associates.%20I%20was%20told%20to%20meet%20the%20district%20judge%20at%20night%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20civil%20judge%20wrote%20in%20her%20letter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EAlthough%20she%20does%20not%20state%20specific%20instances%20or%20names%20the%20accused%2C%20her%20letter%20provides%20a%20clear%20glimpse%20of%20the%20distressing%20experience%20she%20had%20to%20go%20through%20in%20order%20to%20seek%20justice%20for%20herself.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EShe%20alleged%20that%20she%20was%20abused%20verbally%20in%20open%20court%20with%20a%20misogynist%20slur%20and%20that%20she%20had%20even%20tried%20to%20kill%20herself%20through%20suicide.%20The%20judge%20reportedly%20endured%20the%20harassment%20and%20abuse%20during%20her%20earlier%20posting%20in%20another%20district%20close%20to%20the%20capital%20Lucknow.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9CI%20have%20been%20sexually%20harassed%20to%20the%20very%20limit.%20I%20have%20been%20treated%20like%20utter%20garbage.%20I%20feel%20like%20an%20unwanted%20insect.%20And%20I%20hoped%20to%20provide%20justice%20to%20others.%20What%20naive%20me!%E2%80%9D%20she%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThe%20woman%20judge%2C%20whose%20identity%20and%20location%20are%20not%20being%20disclosed%20to%20protect%20her%20privacy%20as%20mandated%20by%20law%2C%20said%20she%20had%C2%A0%20complained%20to%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20the%20Allahabad%20high%20court%20and%20the%20administrative%20judge%20in%202022%20but%20that%20no%20action%20has%20been%20taken%20till%20date.%20Nobody%20had%20even%20bothered%20to%20ask%20why%20she%20was%20distressed%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EIn%20July%2C%202023%20she%20complained%20to%20the%20Internal%20Complaints%20Committee%20(ICC)%20of%20the%20high%20court%20but%20it%20%E2%80%9Ctook%20six%20months%20and%20a%20thousand%20emails%E2%80%9D%20just%20to%20start%20an%20enquiry%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20proposed%20enquiry%20is%20also%20a%20farce%20and%20a%20sham.%20The%20witnesses%20in%20the%20enquiry%20are%20immediate%20subordinates%20of%20the%20district%20judge%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said%2C%20arguing%20that%20for%20a%20fair%20enquiry%20the%20witnesses%20ought%20not%20to%20be%20in%20the%20administrative%20control%20of%20the%20accused.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9CHow%20the%20committee%20expects%20the%20witnesses%20to%20depose%20against%20their%20boss%20is%20beyond%20my%20understanding.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThe%20civil%20judge%20said%20she%20had%20requested%20that%20the%20accused%20district%20judge%20be%20transferred%20during%20the%20pendency%20of%20the%20enquiry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EPetition%20dismissed%20at%20SC%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EShe%20then%20approached%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20with%20her%20prayer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EA%20bench%20of%20Justices%20Hrishikesh%20Roy%20and%20Sandeep%20Mehta%20on%20December%2013%20dismissed%20a%20writ%20petition%20filed%20by%20her%20saying%20that%20her%20matter%20was%20already%20under%20the%20process%20of%20the%20ICC.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThe%20court%20said%2C%E2%80%9D%20Since%20the%20internal%20complaints%20committee%20concerned%20is%20already%20in%20session%20of%20the%20matter%20and%20a%20resolution%20is%20already%20passed%20which%20is%20pending%20approval%20of%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20the%20Allahabad%20High%20Court%2C%20we%20see%20no%20reason%20to%20entertain%20this%20writ%20petition%20under%20Article%2032%20of%20the%20Constitution.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EShe%20expressed%20dismay%20at%20the%20SC%E2%80%99s%20dismissal%20of%20her%20petition%20and%20alleged%20that%20her%20plea%20was%20dismissed%20in%20eight%20seconds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9D%20I%20thought%20that%20the%20highest%20court%20will%20definitely%20hear%20such%20a%20straight%20forward%20benign%20prayer.%20What%20did%20I%20know%3F%20My%20writ%20petition%20was%20dismissed%20in%208%20seconds%20without%20any%20hearing%20and%20consideration%20of%20my%20prayers%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said%20in%20the%20open%20letter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThe%20judge%20expressed%20her%20scepticism%20about%20a%20fair%20enquiry%20in%20her%20matter.%20%E2%80%9CWhat%20Justice%20will%20I%20give%20to%20others%20when%20I%20am%20myself%20hopeless%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EIn%20her%20letter%2C%20the%20judge%20also%20issued%20a%20message%20to%20working%20women%20in%20the%20country%2C%20warning%20them%20of%20the%20tall%20order%20of%20their%20fight%20against%20the%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9CI%20wish%20to%20tell%20all%20the%20working%20women%20in%20India%3A%20Learn%20to%20live%20with%20sexual%20harassment.%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20truth%20of%20our%20lives.%20The%20POSH%20ACT%20is%20a%20big%20wholesome%20lie%20told%20to%20us.%20No%20one%20listens%2C%20no%20one%20bothers%E2%80%A6.And%20I%20am%20judge.%20I%20could%20not%20even%20a%20muster%20a%20fair%20enquiry%20for%20myself%2C%20let%20alone%20justice.%20I%20advise%20all%20women%20to%20learn%20to%20be%20a%20toy%2C%20or%20a%20non-living%20thing.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702724067000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flabour%2Fcivil-judges-letter-cji-sexual-harassment%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22'The%20POSH%20ACT%20is%20a%20big%20wholesome%20lie%20told%20to%20us.%20No%20one%20listens%2C%20no%20one%20bothers...And%20I%20am%20judge.'%22%2C%22author%22%3