ould%20leave%20for%20a%20holiday%20tip%2C%20according%20to%20Nick%20Leighton%2C%20etiquette%20expert%20and%20co-host%20of%20advice%20podcast%20%26quot%3BWere%20You%20Raised%20By%20Wolves%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWho%20to%20tip%20and%20how%20much%20to%20tip%20are%20made%20up%20of%20a%20constellation%20of%20factors%2C%20including%20the%20nature%20and%20length%20of%20the%20relationship%20with%20a%20person%20and%20what's%20considered%20'typical'%20in%20your%20area%2C%26quot%3B%20Leighton%20wrote%20to%20Business%20Insider%20by%20email.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20those%20who%20might%20need%20a%20little%20more%20help%20figuring%20out%20what%20makes%20for%20an%20appropriate%20tip%2C%20BI%20chatted%20with%20etiquette%20experts%20to%20put%20together%20a%20helpful%20holiday%20tip%20guide.%20The%20following%20are%20suggested%20guidelines%2C%20but%20if%20your%20finances%20are%20tight%2C%20there%20is%20flexibility%20to%20%26quot%3Bwork%20with%20what%20you%20can%20in%20your%20own%20budget%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Swann.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EFor%20your%20babysitter%2C%20housekeeper%2C%20or%20nanny%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%227257%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20babysitter%20plays%20with%20a%20child%20at%20the%20%26quot%3BNoemi%20Rigolo%20comme%20la%20vie%26quot%3B%20nursery%20in%20Roubaix%2C%20northern%20France%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F657cc85450edbc52a864fe1f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224838%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20recommended%20tip%20for%20a%20babysitter%20is%20a%20single%20visit's%20pay.%3Cp%3ESameer%20Al-Doumy%2F%20AFP%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20visit's%20pay%20for%20your%20babysitter%20or%20housekeeper%20would%20be%20a%20good%20holiday%20tip%2C%20according%20to%20etiquette%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmister-manners.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eexpert%3C%2Fa%3E%20Thomas%20P.%20Farley%2C%20or%20%26quot%3BMister%20Manners.%26quot%3B%20For%20a%20live-in%20nanny%2C%20the%20bar%20is%20a%20little%20higher%20so%20a%20good%20tip%20might%20be%20closer%20to%20one%20week's%20pay%20or%20even%20up%20to%20one%20month's%20pay%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20have%20a%20dog%20walker%20or%20groomer%2C%20or%20someone%20who%20cleans%20your%20pool%20or%20maintains%20your%20lawn%2C%20aim%20for%20the%20cash%20equivalent%20of%20one%20service%2C%20says%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdianegottsman.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDiane%20Gottsman%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20an%20etiquette%20expert%20and%20founder%20of%20The%20Protocol%20School%20of%20Texas.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EFor%20your%20doormen%20or%20superintendent%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Doorman%20Aneudy%20Santana%20works%20at%20his%20building%20on%20the%20Upper%20East%20Side%20of%20Manhattan%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F657cca407a3c8094d5ddc355%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETips%20for%20doormen%20can%20vary%20depending%20on%20the%20circumstances.%3Cp%3ESpencer%20Platt%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ETips%20for%20doormen%20vary%20based%20on%20where%20you%20live%20and%20how%20often%20you%20interact%20with%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20building%20with%20multiple%20doormen%2C%20you're%20probably%20going%20to%20want%20to%20tip%20%2420%20to%20%24100%20per%20doorman%2C%20says%20Gottsman%2C%20though%20you%20can%20go%20up%20to%20%26quot%3Bhundreds%20of%20dollars%20sometimes%20per%20doorman%26quot%3B%20in%20a%20luxury%20building%20in%20a%20big%20city%2C%20says%20Farley%2C%20noting%20that%20tips%20here%20still%20vary%20from%20context%20to%20context.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20those%20who%20live%20in%20a%20smaller%20building%20without%20a%20doorman%2C%20but%20have%20a%20building%20superintendent%20who%20performs%20small%20services%20from%20time%20to%20time%2C%20be%20as%20generous%20as%20your%20budget%20allows%2C%20Farley%20said.%20%26quot%3BIf%20your%20budget%20is%20tight%2C%20and%20perhaps%20this%20is%20not%20a%20high-service%20building%2C%20perhaps%20the%20tip%20for%20the%20super%20is%20%2450%20or%20%24100%2C%26quot%3B%20Farley%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20if%20you're%20in%20a%20luxury%20building%20where%20your%20super%20is%20doing%20much%20more%20work%20for%20you%2C%20and%20you're%20not%20tipping%20on%20each%20occasion%2C%20then%20it's%20worth%20being%20%26quot%3Bespecially%20generous%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EConsider%20aiming%20for%20%2420%20to%20%24100%20for%20a%20maintenance%20worker%20in%20your%20building%2C%20and%20%2410%20to%20%2450%20for%20a%20garage%20attendant%20if%20you%20have%20one%2C%20says%20Gottsman.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EFor%20your%20hairdresser%2C%20colorist%2C%20manicurist%2C%20or%20personal%20services%20provider%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20manicurist%20files%20a%20customer's%20nails.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F657ccb047a3c8094d5ddc3ab%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222308%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EHoliday%20tips%20for%20workers%20like%20manicurists%20can%20be%20equal%20to%20the%20cost%20of%20one%20visit.%3Cp%3EJim%20Young%2FReuters%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20if%20you're%20giving%20out%20a%20tip%20to%20your%20hairdresser%20or%20manicurist%20every%20time%20you%20visit%20the%20salon%2C%20Farley%20still%20suggests%20giving%20them%20a%20holiday%20tip.%20%26quot%3BIn%20this%20category%2C%20the%20personal%20services%20category%2C%20your%20gratuity%20should%20be%20the%20cost%20of%20one%20visit%2C%26quot%3B%20Farley%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20rule%20of%20thumb%20also%20extends%20to%20workers%20like%20massage%20therapists%20or%20personal%20trainers%2C%20says%20Gottsman.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EThere%20are%20some%20workers%20you%20shouldn't%20(or%20legally%20can't)%20tip%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%227360%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Mail%20carrier%20Tiffany%20Sufficool%20delivers%20the%20mail%20during%20subzero%20temperatures%20carried%20by%20the%20polar%20votex%20in%20Fargo%2C%20North%20Dakota%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F657cce4050edbc52a86500d3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224912%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ENon-cash%20gifts%20may%20be%20the%20best%20choice%20for%20workers%20like%20mail%20carriers.%20%3Cp%3EDan%20Koeck%2FReuters%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20include%20your%20doctor%2C%20lawyer%2C%20accountant%2C%20child's%20teacher%2C%20and%20mail%20carrier.%20If%20you%20want%20to%20express%20your%20gratitude%20to%20these%20workers%2C%20a%20non-cash%20gift%20would%20be%20more%20appropriate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrash%20collectors%20may%20be%20prohibited%20from%20accepting%20tips%20in%20certain%20municipalities%2C%20so%20check%20your%20local%20regulations%2C%20but%20otherwise%2C%20%2410%20to%20%2425%20per%20person%20is%20good%2C%20according%20to%20Gottsman.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20end%20of%20the%20day%2C%20your%20tipping%20amount%20really%20boils%20down%20to%20a%20few%20key%20factors%2C%20for%20all%20of%20the%20workers%20you%20regularly%20interact%20with%20throughout%20the%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20sliding%20scale%20depending%20on%20the%20relationship%20you%20have%2C%20your%20budget%2C%20and%20what%20they've%20done%20for%20you%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Gottsman.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you're%20in%20extenuating%20financial%20circumstances%2C%20do%20your%20best.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20give%20them%20what%20you%20can%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Swann.%20%26quot%3BIt%20might%20be%20half%20of%20that.%20It%20might%20be%20a%20third%20of%20that.%20But%20you%20do%20what%20you%20can.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20end%2C%20it's%20really%20the%20thought%20that%20counts.%20The%20holidays%20are%20a%20time%20to%20%26quot%3Brecognize%20not%20just%20our%20loved%20