mportantly%2C%20I've%20seen%20the%20impact%20her%20approach%20has%20had%20on%20my%20closet.%20I%20use%20these%20three%20principles%20to%20stay%20more%20stylish%20than%20I've%20ever%20been%20before.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EKnow%20your%20color.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Color%20is%20the%20quickest%20way%20to%20make%20or%20break%20your%20outfit.%20To%20find%20the%20right%20colors%20for%20you%2C%20hold%20fabrics%20under%20your%20chin%20to%20see%20what%20makes%20your%20face%20light%20up.%20Don't%20overthink%20it.%20My%20colors%20are%20muted%20autumn%20hues%2C%20so%20when%20I%20walk%20into%20a%20store%2C%20I%20can%20reach%20immediately%20for%20items%20in%20that%20palette.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHighlight%20what%20makes%20you%20unique.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20One%20of%20the%20principles%20of%20Kibbe%20Body%20Types%20is%20highlighting%20your%20distinct%20features%20rather%20than%20hiding%20them.%20I%20have%20long%20limbs%2C%20so%20I%20dress%20in%20structured%20fabrics%20with%20long%20lines.%20Many%20women%20have%20broad%20shoulders%20that%20they're%20tempted%20to%20hide.%20Instead%2C%20emphasize%20them%20with%20wide%20necklines%20and%20fabrics%20that%20drape%20over%20your%20shoulders.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDress%20for%20your%20life.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Sometimes%2C%20fashion%20can%20look%20unobtainable.%20As%20a%20middle-aged%20woman%20living%20in%20a%20rural%20area%2C%20I'm%20never%20going%20to%20wear%20the%20same%20items%20as%20Kylie%20Jenner%20and%20other%20starlets.%20But%20I%20can%20look%20just%20as%20good%20as%20them%20%E2%80%94%20in%20my%20own%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EGetting%20dressed%20in%20the%20morning%20isn't%20a%20hassle%20anymore.%20My%20clothing%20items%20complement%20each%20other%20and%20my%20body%2C%20so%20I%20know%20I%20can%20reach%20for%20anything%20in%20my%20closet%20and%20look%20great.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.busin