ined%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenai-cofounder-greg-brockman-responds-elon-musk-woke-criticism-chatgpt-2023-3%23%3A~%3Atext%3DMusk%2520called%2520the%2520chatbot%2527s%2520refusal%2C%252C%2520lie%2520%25E2%2580%2593%2520is%2520deadly.%2522%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EChatGPT%20is%20too%20%26quot%3Bwoke%2C%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20said%20that%20training%20AI%20to%20be%20politically%20correct%20is%20%26quot%3Bdeadly.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BGrok%20has%20real-time%20access%20to%20info%20via%20the%20X%20platform%2C%20which%20is%20a%20massive%20advantage%20over%20other%20models%2C%26quot%3B%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Felonmusk%2Fstatus%2F1720660977786433810%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMusk%20wrote%20on%20X%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20also%20based%20%26amp%3B%20loves%20sarcasm.%20I%20have%20no%20idea%20who%20could%20have%20guided%20it%20this%20way.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20Musk%20appears%20to%20be%20taking%20Grok%20very%20seriously.%20So%20far%2C%20xAI%20has%20raised%20closed%20to%20%24135%20million%20in%20equity%20financing%20and%20aims%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-seeks-raise-one-billion-for-xai-openai-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eraise%20up%20to%20%241%20billion%20for%20xAI%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEarly%20access%20to%20Grok%20is%20now%20available%20to%20users%20who%20purchased%20the%20premium%20version%20of%20X%2C%20formerly%20known%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-twitter%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETwitter%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHere's%20how%20to%20use%20Grok%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E1)%20Subscribe%20to%20X%20Premium%2B.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22289%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20left%20sidebar%20for%20X%2C%20formerly%20known%20as%20Twitter%2C%20that%20includes%20G