%20%26quot%3BMy%20son%20is%20not%20an%20offender.%20We%20will%20go%20to%20court.%20You%20can%20ask%20the%20villagers%3B%20my%20son%20was%20not%20like%20this%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELalit%20Jha's%20mother%20echoed%20the%20sentiment%2C%20describing%20her%20son%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bvery%20good%20boy.%26quot%3B%20She%20added%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20not%20able%20to%20understand.%20We%20had%20no%20information%20about%20this%20matter.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoth%20parents%20are%20resolute%20in%20their%20belief%20that%20Jha%20is%20innocent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Kolkata%20coaching%20centre%2C%20where%20Lalit%20Jha%20teaches%2C%20has%20also%20vouched%20for%20his%20character.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELalit%20Jha%20-%20the%20alleged%20mastermind%20behind%20the%20Parliament%20security%20breach%20-%20burned%20the%20mobile%20phones%20of%20four%20accomplices%20in%20a%20bid%20to%20destroy%20evidence%2C%20Delhi%20Police%20sources%20told%20NDTV.%20Jha%2C%20who%20surrendered%20to%20the%20cops%20on%20Thursday%2C%20said%20he%20had%20kept%20the%20mobile%20phones%20of%20the%20two%20men%20who%20popped%20yellow%20smoke%20canisters%20inside%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20and%20the%20man%20and%20woman%20did%20so%20outside%20Parliament.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJha%20told%20police%20he%20filmed%20the%20latter%20incident%2C%20uploaded%20the%20clip%20to%20Instagram%2C%20and%20sent%20it%20to%20a%20Kolkata-based%20NGO%20to%20ensure%20media%20coverage%2C%20before%20fleeing%20the%20scene.%20On%20the%20run%20for%2048%20hours%2C%20he%20claimed%20to%20have%20travelled%20to%20Nagaur%20in%20Rajasthan%20to%20stay%20with%20two%20friends.%20Lalit%20Jha%20and%20another%20man%2C%20Mahesh%2C%20returned%20to%20Delhi%20Thursday%20evening%2C%20after%20which%20Jha%20gave%20himself%20up%20at%20a%20police%20station%20in%20central%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702717080000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2Fapbffss8_lalit-jha-parliament-security-breach_625x300_