%20the%20T20%20franchise%20league.%20Rohit%20Sharma%20commands%20a%20huge%20fan%20following%20and%20his%20removal%20as%20the%20skipper%20was%20met%20with%20some%20strong%20reactions%20from%20Mumbai%20Indian%20supporters.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20a%20new%20report%20has%20claimed%20that%20Rohit%20Sharma%20was%20informed%20about%20the%20need%20of%20change%20in%20Mumbai%20Indians%20captaincy%20around%20the%20start%20of%20the%20ODI%20Cricket%20World%20Cup%202023%2C%20which%20began%C2%A0%20in%20the%20first%20week%20of%20October.%20According%20to%20the%20report%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fsports%2Fcricket%2Fmumbai-indians-name-hardik-pandya-as-captain-for-ipl-2024-instead-of-rohit-sharma-9069835%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EIndian%20Express%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Rohit%20Sharma%20agreed%20to%20play%20under%20Hardik%20Pandya%20in%20IPL%202024.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHardik%20Pandya%2C%20who%20had%20left%20Mumbai%20Indians%20to%20join%20Gujarat%20Titans%20in%202022%2C%20was%20bought%20back%20ahead%20of%20the%20IPL%202024.%20The%20report%20claimed%20that%20Hardik%20Pandya's%20condition%20was%20that%20he%20would%20return%20to%20Mumbai%20Indians%20if%20he%20is%20made%20the%20captain.%20The%20MI%20management%20then%20decided%20on%20the%20way%20forward%20and%20made%20Rohit%20Sharma%20aware%20of%20their%20decision.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMumbai%20Indians%20(MI)%20on%20Friday%20named%20Hardik%20Pandya%20as%20their%20captain%20ahead%20of%20the%20Indian%20Premier%20League%20(IPL)%202024.%20Hardik%20replaced%20a%20highly-successful%20Rohit%20Sharma%2C%20who%20led%20the%20IPL%20giants%20to%20five%20trophies.%20The%20announcement%20from%20Mumbai%20Indians%20came%20after%20Hardik%20made%20a%20return%20to%20the%20franchise%20last%20month%2C%20following%20a%20high-profile%20trade%20from%20Gujarat%20Titans%2C%20whom%20he%20led%20in%20the%20past%20two%20seasons.%20After%20announcing%20the%20news%20of%20the%20captaincy%20change%2C%20MI%20put%20a%20heartfelt%20post%20on%20social%20media%20for%20Rohit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRo%2C%20In%202013%20you%20took%20over%20as%20captain%20of%20MI.%20You%20asked%20us%20to%20Believe.%20In%20victories%20%26amp%3B%20defeats%2C%20you%20asked%20us%20to%20Smile.%2010%20years%20%26amp%3B%206%20trophies%20later%2C%20here%20we%20are.%20Our%20forever%20captain%20your%20legacy%20will%20be%20etched%20in%20Blue%20%26amp%3B%20Gold.%20Thank%20you%2C%20Captain%20RO%2C%26quot%3B%20wrote%20MI%20on%20X%2C%20formerly%20Twitter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20in%20a%20statement%20on%20Friday%2C%20Mumbai%20Indians%20said%20the%20change%20in%20leadership%20was%20part%20of%20their%20future%20planning%20and%20thanked%20Rohit%20for%20his%20exemplary%20service%20to%20the%20franchise.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMumbai%20Indians%20are%20the%20most%20successful%20IPL%20franchise%20alongside%20Chennai%20Super%20Kings%20who%20both%20have%20won%20five%20titles%20each.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERohit%2C%20who%20recently%20led%20India%20to%20the%20ODI%20World%20Cup%20final%2C%20had%20been%20captaining%20the%20franchise%20since%202013%20when%20they%20lifted%20first%20of%20their%20five%20IPL%20trophies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20other%20titles%20under%20Rohit's%20captaincy%20came%20in%202015%2C%202017%2C%202019%20and%202020.%20Mumbai%20Indians%20had%20made%20it%20to%20the%20play-offs%20in%20IPL%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20express%20our%20gratitude%20to%20Rohit%20Sharma%20for%20his%20exceptional%20leadership%3B%20his%20tenure%20as%20the%20captain%20of%20the%20Mumbai%20Indians%20since%202013%20has%20been%20nothing%20short%20of%20extraordinary%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Mahela%20Jayawardene%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F244-mahela-jayawardene-playerprofile%5C%22%3EMahela%20Jayawardene%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20MI's%20Global%20Head%20of%20Performance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20PTI%20inputs%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%