at%20scares%20away%20the%20others%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20popularity%20quickly%20became%20too%20much%20to%20handle%20and%20Folderol%20had%20to%20start%20setting%20rules.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222125%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Folderol%20no%20TikTok%20sign%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6575b4880ec98e92f74deed7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222833%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EFolderol's%20%26quot%3Bno%20TikTok%26quot%3B%20sign.%3Cp%3EBusiness%20Insider%20%2F%20Folderol%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20owners%20banned%20people%20from%20eating%20and%20drinking%20on%20the%20road%20outside%2C%20put%20up%20a%20%26quot%3Bno%20TikTok%26quot%3B%20sign%2C%20and%20even%20hired%20a%20bouncer%20to%20control%20the%20crowds.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20rules%20aimed%20to%20cut%20down%20the%20amount%20of%20%26quot%3Bviral%20posters%20sitting%20outside%20eating%20a%20scoop%20of%20olive%20oil%20ice%20cream%20and%20a%20glass%20of%20orange%20wine%20not%20even%20taking%20any%20pleasure%20in%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Compagnon%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20bouncer%2C%20who%20prefers%20to%20be%20known%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bgreeter%2C%26quot%3B%20wasn't%20just%20to%20deter%20the%20TikTokers%2C%20Compagnon%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20had%20a%20lot%20of%20issues%20over%20the%20summer%20with%20crowds.%20It's%20a%20really%20quiet%20street%2C%20so%20as%20soon%20as%20it's%20past%209%20p.m.%20and%20there's%20noise%20the%20neighbors%20were%20going%20crazy%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BThe%20cops%20were%20coming%20because%20of%20the%20noise%20complaints.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Bouncer%2Fgreeter%20outside%20Folderol%20wine%20bar%20in%20Paris%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6575b15b7a3c8094d5db728e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EFolderol's%20%26quot%3Bgreeter%26quot%3B%20outside%20the%20shop%20in%20Paris.%3Cp%3EBusiness%20Insider%2FFolderol%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20sudden%20online%20explosion%20came%20as%20a%20complete%20surprise%20to%20the%20couple%20running%20the%20trendy%20spot.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20do%20extraordinarily%20little%20social%20media%20posting%2C%26quot%3B%20Compagnon%20said.%20%26quot%3BOur%20presence%20is%20basically%20nonexistent.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20bar%20was%20also%20just%20not%20set%20up%20for%20the%20attention%20it%20received.%20The%20kitchen%20was%20too%20small%20to%20prep%20accordingly%20and%20staffers%20were%20overwhelmed%20by%20the%20demand%20and%20bored%20by%20the%20repetitive%20nature%20of%20service.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Orange%20wine%20in%20a%20glass%20at%20Folderol%20Paris%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6575b4dc7a3c8094d5db72f3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222268%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20glass%20of%20orange%20wine%20at%20Folderol.%3Cp%3EBusiness%20Insider%2FFolderol%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20a%20double-edged%20sword%2C%20Compagnon%20said%2C%20who%20is%20not%20immune%20to%20the%20financial%20gain%20the%20viral%20success%20has%20brought%20the%20wine%20bar.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20like%20saying%20no%20to%20money%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20of%20his%20attempts%20to%20dispel%20the%20influencers.%20%26quot%3BWe%20don't%20enforce%20it%2C%20really.%20It's%20just%20about%20trying%20to%20balance%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20of%20the%20attempts%20have%20also%20backfired%2C%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20people%20have%20been%20keen%20to%20break%20the%20new%20rules.%20A%20TikTok%20video%20shot%20at%20Folderol%20captioned%2C%20%26quot%3BIf%20you%20tell%20me%20not%20to%20do%20something%20I'll%20just%20want%20to%20do%20it%20more%2C%26quot%3B%20demonstrates%20his%20point.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECompagn