Cp%3ETalking%20about%20the%20match%2C%20Deepti%20Sharma%20played%20the%20enforcer's%20role%20to%20perfection%20for%20the%20second%20time%20in%20as%20many%20days%20as%20the%20dominant%20India%20Women%20scripted%20a%20historic%20347-run%20victory%20over%20England%20on%20the%20third%20day%20of%20the%20one-off%20Test%20on%20Saturday.%20India%20set%20in%20motion%20the%20hunt%20for%20triumph%20while%20declaring%20their%20second%20innings%20closed%20at%20the%20overnight%20score%20of%20186%20for%206%2C%20leaving%20England%20to%20climb%20a%20huge%20mountain%20of%20479%20runs%20in%20their%20second%20innings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20bowlers%20led%20by%20off-spinner%20Deepti%20Sharma%20(4%2F32)%20and%20pacer%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Pooja%20Vastrakar%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F117789-pooja-vastrakar-playerprofile%5C%22%3EPooja%20Vastrakar%3C%2Fa%3E%20(3%2F23)%20then%20bundled%20out%20England%20for%20131%20to%20celebrate%20a%20victory%20which%20now%20stands%20as%20the%20biggest%20in%20terms%20of%20runs%20in%20the%20history%20of%20women's%20Test%20cricket.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20course%20of%20the%20last%20three%20days%20the%20Indians%20did%20not%20show%20any%20rust%20of%20not%20having%20played%20Test%20cricket%20in%20two%20years%2C%20and%20a%20first%20at%20home%20after%20nine%20years%2C%20while%20being%20at%20their%20ruthless%20best.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20for%20all%20that%20slew%20of%20records%2C%20the%20Harmanpreet%20Kaur-led%20side%20should%20thank%20Deepti%20(8-2-32-4)%20who%20was%20in%20her%20elements%20after%20that%20sensational%205%20for%20seven%20in%20the%20first%20innings%2C%20as%20England%20lacked%20gumption%20to%20fight%20even%20on%20a%20pitch%20that%20appeared%20to%20be%20far%20more%20gentle.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20did%20not%20have%20to%20wait%20for%20long%20for%20the%20first%20breakthrough%20this%20morning.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20came%20in%20the%20form%20of%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Tammy%20Beaum