%20Gaza%20amid%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20operation%20against%20Hamas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20three%20hostages%20were%20killed%20in%20the%20Gaza%20City%20district%20of%20Shijaiyah.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20post%20on%20X%2C%20formerly%20Twitter%2C%20the%20IDF%20said%20its%20soldiers%20mistakenly%20identified%20three%20Israeli%20hostages%20as%20a%20threat.%20%E2%80%9CAs%20a%20result%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20post%20added%2C%20the%20soldiers%20%E2%80%9Cfired%20toward%20them%20and%20the%20hostages%20were%20killed.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwo%20of%20the%20victims%20were%20identified%20as%20Yotam%20Haim%2C%20who%20was%20taken%20from%20Kibbutz%20Kfar%20Aza%2C%20and%20Samer%20Talalka%2C%20who%20was%20taken%20from%20Kibbutz%20Nir%20Am.%20The%20IDF%20said%20it%20was%20withholding%20the%20third%20hostage%E2%80%99s%20name%20at%20the%20family%E2%80%99s%20request.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bodies%20have%20been%20returned%20to%20Israel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20a%20tragic%20incident%2C%20the%20army%20bears%20full%20responsibility%2C%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%C2%A0Israeli%20military%20spokesman%20Daniel%20Hagari%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20IDF%20said%20it%20was%C2%A0investigating%20the%20incident.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EProtests%20in%20Israel%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EScores%20of%20people%20took%20to%20the%20streets%20in%20Tel%20Aviv%20to%20protest%20the%20death%20of%20the%20three%20hostages%20mistakenly%20killed%20by%20Israeli%20soldiers%20in%20Gaza%2C%20according%20to%20media%20reports.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELocal%20media%20reports%20and%20images%20on%20television%20showed%20protesters%20blocking%20a%20main%20street%20in%20the%20centre%20of%20the%20city%2C%20demanding%20the%20government%20take%20immediate%20action%20to%20secure%20the%20release%20of%20the%20hostages.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CTheir%20time%20is%20running%20out!%20Bring%20them%20home%20now!%E2%80%9D%20the%20crowd%20was%20heard%20chanting%2C%20according%20to%20a%20report%20by%20the%3Cem%