e%20canisters%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESimha%20is%20a%20two-term%20MP%20from%20Mysore-Kodagu%20in%20Karnataka%2C%20having%20won%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20in%20both%202014%20and%202019.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOpposition%20MPs%20have%20questioned%20why%20no%20action%20was%20taken%20against%20Simha%20while%2014%20opposition%20MPs%20were%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fparliament-security-breach-rajnath-singh-opposition-statement-amit-shah%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Esuspended%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3Eon%20Thursday%20for%20protesting%20against%20the%20security%20breach%20and%20demanding%20a%20statement%20by%20Union%20home%20minister%20Amit%20Shah.%20They%20have%20also%20questioned%20why%20TMC%20MP%20Mahua%20Moitra%20was%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fmahua-moitra-tmc-lok-sabha-ethic-panel-expel-adjourn%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eexpelled%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20for%20sharing%20her%20password%20on%20grounds%20of%20national%20security%2C%20but%20no%20action%20has%20been%20taken%20against%20Simha.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EUnder%20fire%20for%20the%20security%20breach%2C%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government%20has%20sought%20to%20list%20other%20security%20breaches%20in%20Parliament%20while%20asking%20the%20opposition%20members%20not%20to%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fparliament-security-breach-rajnath-singh-opposition-statement-amit-shah%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9Cpoliticise%E2%80%9D%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3Ethe%20issue.%20The%20Union%20government%20or%20the%20BJP%20is%20yet%20to%20issue%20a%20statement%20on%20Simha.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20six%20people%20(Sagar%20Sharma%20and%20Manoranjan%20D%2C%20who%20entered%20the%20Parliamentary%20premises%2C%20Neelam%20Azad%20and%20Amol%20Shinde%20who%20were%20shouting%20slogans%20outside%20the%20Parliament%2C%20and%20their%20associates%20Lalit%20Jha%20and%20Vicky%20Sharma)%20who%20were%20allegedly%20involved%20in%20the%20incident%20%E2%80%93%20as%20a%20protest%20to%20highlight%20issues%20of%20unemployment%2C%20farmers%E2%80%99%20unrest%2C%20and%20the%20ethnic%20clashes%20in%20Manipur%20%E2%80%93%20have%20all%20since%20been%20arrested.%20They%20are%20also%20facing%20charges%20under%20the%20draconian%20terror%20law%20Unlawful%20Activities%20(Prevention)%20Act%20(UAPA).%20Simha%2C%20however%2C%20has%20yet%20to%20face%20any%20action.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESimha%E2%80%99s%20name%20first%20came%20up%20after%20BSP%20MP%20Danish%20Ali%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FPTI_News%2Fstatus%2F1734846771568808416%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Esaid%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20moments%20after%20the%20incident%20on%20Wednesday%20that%20while%20he%20apprehended%20Sagar%20Sharma%20along%20with%20security%20staff%2C%20he%20discovered%20a%20pass%20that%20included%20an%20authorisation%20signature%20by%20Simha.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELater%2C%20Ali%20also%20tweeted%20a%20picture%20of%20the%20pass%20that%20bore%20Simha%E2%80%99s%20name.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EIn%20a%20chilling%20reminder%20to%20the%20Parliament%20attack%2021%20years%20back%20on%20the%20same%20day%20(Dec%2013)%2C%20a%20man%20jumped%20from%20visitors%E2%80%99%20gallery%20into%20Lok%20Sabha%20MPs%20area.%20The%20breach%20could%E2%80%99ve%20put%20lives%20of%20MPs%20in%20danger.%20It%20has%20exposed%20chinks%20in%20the%2056inch%20armour.%20The%20man%20was%20a%20guest%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FBJP4India%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40BJP4India%3C%2Fa%3E%20MP.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FqhPX4C4Dia%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FqhPX4C4Dia%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20Kunwar%20Danish%20Ali%20(%40KDanishAli)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FKDanishAli%2Fstatus%2F1734872292323156050%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EDecember%2013%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESimha%20has%20said%20to%20parliamentary%20affairs%20ministry%20Pralhad%20Joshi%20that%20he%20knew%20Manoranjan%20D.%E2%80%99s%20father%2C%20reported%20the%20news%20agency%20Press%20Trust%20of%20India.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20report%20also%20said%20that%20Manoranjan%20had%20been%20pursuing%20the%20BJP%20MP%20for%20a%20while%20to%20get%20a%20pass%20to%20visit%20the%20new%20parliament%20building%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EManoranjan%E2%80%99s%20father%20Devaraj%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Findia%2Fmanoranjan-parliament-security-breach-farmer-son-engineering-graduate-9066737%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Etold%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ethe%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E%20Indian%20Expres%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Es%20that%20Simha%20is%20their%20local%20MP%20and%20they%20share%20a%20good%20relationship%20with%20him.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20is%20not%20the%20first%20time%20that%20Simha%20has%20courted%20controversy.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EFormer%20journalist%20who%20made%20his%20Hindutva%20leanings%20evident%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESimha%2C%20a%20former%20Kannada%20language%20journalist%2C%20is%20known%20in%20his%20region%20for%20provocative%20statements%2C%20especially%20those%20which%20directly%20or%20indirectly%20attack%20the%20Muslim%20community.%20Working%20as%20a%20journalist%20until%202014%2C%20when%20he%20became%20an%20MP%20for%20the%20first%20time%2C%20he%20had%20made%20his%20Hindutva%20leanings%20evident.%20He%20worked%20under%20editor%20Vishweswar%20Bhat%20who%20runs%20the%20Kannada%20daily%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EViswavani%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20known%20for%20its%20extremist%20Hindutva%20positions.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EYet%2C%20Simha%20shot%20to%20fame%20first%20in%202010%20when%20his%20book%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E%20Mining%20Mafia%3A%20Ivaryaaru%20Gottenu%2C%20Ivara%20Kathe%20Helaleenu%20(Mining%20Mafia%3A%20Who%20Are%20They%3F%20Do%20You%20Know%20Their%20Story%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E)%20became%20a%20talking%20point.%20The%20book%20sought%20to%20expose%20the%20Bellary%20mining%20mafia%20helmed%20by%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.outlookindia.com%2Fmagazine%2Fstory%2Fthe-reddy-brothers-of-bellary%2F262757%5C%22%3EReddy%20brothers%3C%2Fa%3E%20who%20were%20then%20in%20the%20BJP.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAhead%20of%20the%202014%20elections%2C%20however%2C%20he%20authored%20another%20book%20that%20brought%20him%20into%20the%20good%20books%20of%20the%20BJP.%20The%20book%20was%20called%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ENarendra%20Modi%3A%20Yaaru%20Tuliyada%20Haadi%20(Narendra%20Modi%3A%20The%20Man%20Who%20Treads%20a%20Unique%20Path%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E).%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20book%20earned%20him%20a%20Lok%20Sabha%20ticket%20from%20the%20BJP%2C%20and%20he%20has%20since%20hardened%20his%20political%20posturing%20against%20minorities.%20He%20won%20from%20his%20seat%20again%20in%202019.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%202015%2C%20Simha%20wrote%20another%20book%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ETipu%20Sultan%3A%20Swatantrya%20Veerana%3F%20(Tipu%20Sultan%3A%20Was%20He%20a%20Freedom%20Fighter%3F)%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20fuelling%20Hindutva%20passions%20in%20the%20political%20campaign%20against%20the%2018th-century%20ruler%20of%20Mysore.%20Each%20of%20his%20political%20interventions%20provided%20ammunition%20to%20the%20Hindutva%20workers%20who%20would%20mouth%20contested%20facts%20from%20his%20books.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F16105013%2Fbooks.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F16105013%2Fbooks.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F16105013%2Fbooks-300x150.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F16105013%2Fbooks-1024x512.jpg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F16105013%2Fbooks-800x400.jpg%20800w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-689422%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22600%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EThree%20books%20authored%20by%20BJP%20MP%20Pratap%20Simha.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESimha%2C%20who%20belongs%20to%20the%20dominant%20Vokkaliga%20community%2C%20is%20known%20as%20one%20of%20the%20most%20polarising%20public%20representatives%20that%20the%20region%20of%20Old%20Mysore%2C%20known%20for%20its%20multiculturalism%2C%20has%20ever%20seen.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESimha%20is%20not%20one%20a%20BJP%20old-timer%20in%20Karnataka%2C%20although%20his%20Hindutva%20leanings%20were%20quite%20well%20known.%20But%20he%20is%20seen%20as%20part%20of%20the%20coterie%20that%20was%20encouraged%20by%20Modi-Shah%E2%80%99s%20efforts%20to%20create%20a%20new%2C%20aggressive%20leadership.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ERecent%20controversies%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20November%202022%20Simha%20threatened%20to%20raze%20the%20structure%20on%20the%20Nanjangud%20Highway%20down%20with%20a%20bulldozer%2C%20as%20the%20domes%20on%20the%20bus%20stand%20%E2%80%9Cresembled%20a%20mosque%E2%80%9D.%20The%20Mysuru%20district%20administration%20subs