uits-over-crashes-123121501345_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Ftesla-autopilot-recall-threatens-its-defence-in-lawsuits-over-crashes-123121501345_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22British%20teen%20Alex%20Batty%20left%20mother%20to%20avoid%20Finland%20move%20-%20French%20officials%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702660603000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F62CF%2Fproduction%2F_132059252_batty-index-2.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fuk-67732226%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Alex%20Batty%20was%20constantly%20on%20the%20move%20since%20going%20missing%20in%202017%2C%20French%20officials%20say.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A312%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fuk-67732226%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-co-uk.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fuk-67732226.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fuk-67732226.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Indian-American%20Lawmakers%20Warn%20of%20'Significant%20Damage'%20Pannun%20Murder%20Plot%20Could%20Pose%20to%20Bilateral%20Ties%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F01141008%2FPannun-FP.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20In%20a%20joint%20statement%2C%20Indian-American%20legislators%20in%20the%20US%20Congress%20have%20cautioned%20that%20relations%20between%20India%20and%20the%20United%20States%20could%20face%20%E2%80%9Csignificant%20damage%E2%80%9D%20if%20there%20is%20not%20enough%20accountability%20for%20allegations%20made%20of%20the%20involvement%20of%20an%20Indian%20government%20official%20in%20a%20plot%20to%20kill%20a%20US%20citizen.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fpannun-assassination-plot-india-enquiry-committee-set-up%5C%22%3ELast%20month%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20US%20federal%20prosecutors%20released%20a%20new%20and%20detailed%20indictment%20of%20an%20Indian%20national%2C%20Nikhil%20Gupta%2C%20for%20attempting%20to%20hire%20a%20hitman%20to%20kill%20a%20Sikh%20separatist.%20The%20indictment%20accused%20an%20unnamed%20but%20identified%20Indian%20government%20official%20(%E2%80%98CC-1%E2%80%99)%20of%20recruiting%20Gupta%20for%20orchestrating%20the%20conspiracy.%20Gupta%20is%20currently%20in%20the%20Czech%20Republic%2C%20facing%20extradition%20proceedings%20initiated%20by%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fkhanna.house.gov%2Fmedia%2Fpress-releases%2Frepresentatives-khanna-bera-jayapal-krishnamoorthi-and-thanedar-celebrate%5C%22%3EThe%20joint%20statement%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20released%20on%20Friday%20on%20behalf%20of%20five%20Indian%20American%20lawmakers%20currently%20serving%20in%20the%20118%3Cspan%3Eth%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Congress%20%E2%80%93%20Ami%20Bera%2C%20Pramila%20Jayapal%2C%20Ro%20Khanna%2C%20Raja%20Krishnamoorthi%20and%20Shri%20Thanedar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20statement%20noted%20that%20they%20had%20received%20a%20closed-door%20classified%20briefing%20from%20the%20US%20administration%20on%20the%20charges.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20appreciate%20the%20Administration%20providing%20us%20a%20classified%20briefing%20on%20the%20Department%20of%20Justice%E2%80%99s%20indictment%20of%20Nikhil%20Gupta%2C%20which%20alleges%20that%20an%20Indian%20government%20official%20engaged%20in%20a%20murder-for-hire%20plot%20of%20an%20American%20citizen%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20reference%20to%20%E2%80%9Cclassified%E2%80%9D%20presumably%20means%20that%20the%20legislators%20have%20been%20read%20in%20to%20more%20details%20about%20the%20plot%2C%20including%20its%20%3Cem%3Edramatis%20personae%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20the%20nature%20of%20the%20evidence%20US%20investigators%20have.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStating%20that%20the%20safety%20and%20well-being%20of%20their%20constituents%20were%20of%20utmost%20priority%2C%20the%20five%20lawmakers%20noted%20that%20the%20%E2%80%9Callegations%20made%20in%20the%20indictment%20are%20deeply%20concerning%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWelcoming%20the%20Indian%20government%E2%80%99s%20decision%20to%20set%20up%20a%20committee%20of%20enquiry%2C%20the%20statement%20said%20that%20it%20was%20%E2%80%9Ccritical%20that%20India%20fully%20investigate%2C%20hold%20those%20responsible%2C%20including%20Indian%20government%20officials%2C%20accountable%2C%20and%20provide%20assurances%20that%20this%20will%20not%20happen%20again%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20also%20cautioned%20that%20if%20there%20was%20no%20proper%20accountability%2C%20this%20would%20impact%20the%20bilateral%20relationship.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20believe%20the%20US%E2%80%93India%20partnership%20has%20made%20a%20meaningful%20impact%20on%20the%20lives%20of%20both%20of%20our%20people%2C%20but%20we%20are%20concerned%20that%20the%20actions%20outlined%20in%20the%20indictment%20could%2C%20if%20not%20appropriately%20addressed%2C%20cause%20significant%20damage%20to%20this%20very%20consequential%20partnership%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20allegations%20came%20on%20the%20heels%20of%20the%20public%20accusation%20made%20by%20Canada%20that%20there%20was%20a%20potential%20link%20of%20Indian%20agents%20to%20the%20June%2018%2C%202023%20killing%20of%20Hardeep%20Singh%20Nijjar%2C%20a%20Canadian%20national%C2%A0%20and%20Sikh%20activist%20who%20was%20declared%20a%20terrorist%20by%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20indictment%20seemed%20to%20indicate%20that%20the%20Indian%20government%20official%20(CC-1)%20was%20linked%20to%20the%20killing%20of%20Nijjar.%20The%20%E2%80%98victim%E2%80%99%20in%20the%20US%20court%20filings%20was%20not%20publicly%20identified%2C%20but%20he%20is%20understood%20to%20be%20Gurpatwant%20Singh%20Pannun%2C%20%E2%80%98General%20Counsel%E2%80%99%20for%20%E2%80%98Sikhs%20for%20Justice%E2%80%99%2C%20which%20is%20banned%20as%20a%20terror%20group%20by%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20India%20had%20reacted%20angrily%20to%20the%20Canadian%20allegations%2C%20New%20Delhi%E2%80%99s%20response%20to%20the%20US%20charges%20has%20been%20substantially%20different.%20India%20announced%20that%20it%20had%20set%20up%20a%20high-level%20committee%20to%20look%20into%20the%20%E2%80%9Cinputs%E2%80%9D%20provided%20by%20US%2C%20which%20it%20continued%20to%20relate%20to%20the%20%E2%80%9Cnexus%20between%20organized%20criminals%2C%20gun%20runners%2C%20terrorists%20and%20others%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702659344000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F01141008%2FPannun-FP.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fpannun-murder-plot-significant-damage-likely-for-bilateral-ties-warn-indian-american-lawmakers%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Five%20US%20Congress%20members%20said%20in%20a%20joint%20statement%20that%20it%20is%20critical%20for%20India%20to%20%26quot%3Bfully%20investigate%20%5Band%5D%20hold%20those%20responsible%2C%20including%20Indian%20government%20officials%2C%20accountable%2C%20and%20provide%20assurances%20that%20this%20will%20not%20happen%20again%E2%80%9D.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fpannun-murder-plot-significant-damage-likely-for-bilateral-ties-warn-indian-american-lawmakers%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Shipping%20giants%20suspend%20all%20journeys%20through%20Red%20Sea%20following%20attacks%20on%20vessels%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702656900000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F23%2F12%2F768x432%2Fskynews-maersk-container-ship_6394060.jpg%3F20231215170056%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fshipping-giant-maersk-suspends-all-journeys-through-red-sea-following-attacks-on-vessels-13031107%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Two%20of%20the%20world's%20biggest%20shipping%20firms%20have%20suspended%20all%20journeys%20through%20the%20Red%20Sea%20following%20a%20surge%20of%20recent%20attacks%20on%20vessels.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A319%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fshipping-giant-maersk-suspends-all-journeys-through-red-sea-following-attacks-on-vessels-13031107%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fshipping-giant-maersk-suspends-all-journeys-through-red-sea-following-attacks-on-vessels-13031107%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fshipping-giant-maersk-suspends-all-journeys-through-red-sea-following-attacks-on-vessels-13031107%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Srinagar%3A%20Prayers%20at%20Jamia%20Masjid%20Barred%20for%2010th%20Consecutive%20Friday%2C%20Mirwaiz%20Put%20Under%20House%20Arrest%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F13155820%2FIMG_0834.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Authorities%20in%20Kashmir%20disallowed%20the%20congregational%20prayers%20at%20the%20historic%20mosque%20Jamia%20Masjid%20in%20Srinagar%20city%20for%20the%20tenth%20consecutive%20Friday%20without%20any%20official%20explanation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20statement%2C%20Anjuman%20Auqaf%20Jama%20Masjid%2C%20the%20managing%20body%20of%20the%2014th-century%20mosque%2C%20said%20that%20authorities%20in%20Srinagar%20also%20put%20moderate%20Hurriyat%20chief%20Mirwaiz%20Umar%20Farooq%20under%20house%20arrest%20on%20Friday%2C%20December%2015.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMirwaiz%2C%20who%20is%20also%20the%20chief%20cleric%20of%20Kashmir%2C%20delivers%20the%20main%20sermon%20at%20the%20mosque%20before%20the%20congregational%20Friday%20prayers%20and%20on%20other%20important%20religious%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CNo%20reason%20is%20provided%20by%20the%20authorities%20for%20these%20restrictions%20and%20curbs%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20managing%20body%20said%20in%20the%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAll%20claims%20of%20so-called%20normalcy%20by%20rulers%20fall%20flat%20by%20such%20anti-people%20measures%2C%E2%80%9D%20Mirwaiz%20said%20in%20the%20statement%2C%20denouncing%20the%20curbs%20while%20accusing%20the%20authorities%20of%20allegedly%20targeting%20Jamia%20Masjid%20%E2%80%9Cagain%20and%20again%20%E2%80%A6.%20to%20cause%20grief%20to%20Muslims%20of%20the%20valley%20and%20show%20them%20their%20place%20in%20%E2%80%98naya%20Kashmir%E2%80%99.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlluding%20to%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)-led%20Centre%2C%20Mirwaiz%20said%20that%20the%20authorities%20should%20%E2%80%9Cstop%20playing%20with%20the%20religious%20sentiments%20of%20the%20Muslims%C2%A0%C2%A0and%20let%20them%20offer%20prayers%20in%20their%20mosques%20without%20hindrance.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CPeople%E2%80%99s%20silence%20and%20endurance%20of%20brazen%20attacks%20on%20their%20religious%20rights%20should%20not%20be%20mistaken%20as%20their%20weakness%20to%20respond%2C%E2%80%9D%20Mirwaiz%2C%20who%20was%20part%20of%20the%202002%20dialogue%20on%20the%20Kashmir%20issue%20with%20Pakistan%20initiated%20by%20the%20BJP-led%20Centre%2C%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20September%20this%20year%2C%20after%20more%20than%20four%20years%2C%20the%20moderate%20Hurriyat%20chief%20was%20released%20from%20%E2%80%98house%20arrest%E2%80%99%20and%20allowed%20to%20deliver%20the%20Friday%20sermon%20at%20the%20mosque%20in%20Nowhatta%20locality%20of%20downtown%20Srinagar%20which%20used%20to%20be%20a%20separatist%20hotbed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMirwaiz%E2%80%99s%20appearance%20at%20the%20mosque%20had%20triggered%20emotional%20scenes%20as%20he%20stood%20to%20address%20the%20worshippers%20for%20the%20first%20time%20after%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20was%20stripped%20of%20its%20special%20status.%20On%20the%20pulpit%2C%20the%20Hurriyat%20leader%20broke%20down%20and%20struggled%20to%20hold%20back%20tears.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20mosque%2C%20which%20is%20thronged%20by%20thousands%20of%20Muslims%20on%20important%20religious%20occasions%2C%20has%20since%20remained%20largely%20out%20of%20bounds%20for%20worshippers%20on%20Fridays%20with%20authorities%20citing%20alleged%20fears%20of%20law-and-order%20disturbances.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMirwaiz%20delivered%20his%20sermon%20at%20the%20mosque%20on%20two%20Fridays%20out%20of%2013%20since%20his%20release%20on%20September%2022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20officials%20have%20reportedly%20justified%20the%20closure%20of%20Jamia%20Masjid%2C%20the%20managing%20body%20of%20the%20mosque%20has%20accused%20the%20authorities%20of%20infringing%20on%20the%20religious%20rights%20of%20the%20people%20of%20Kashmir%20under%20the%20garb%20of%20security%20concerns.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20decision%20to%20close%20the%20historical%20mosque%20comes%20at%20a%20time%20when%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20upheld%20the%20Union%20government%E2%80%99s%20controversial%20August%205%2C%202019%20decision%20of%20reading%20down%20Article%20370%20and%20downgrading%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20into%20two%20Union%20territories.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20month%2C%20authorities%20disallowed%20Friday%20prayers%20at%20the%20mosque%20amid%20reported%20apprehensions%20that%20worshippers%20might%20stage%20protests%20or%20take%20out%20demonstrations%20in%20support%20of%20Gaza%20and%20against%20Israel%20by%20sealing%20the%20gates.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20some%20Kashmir-based%20preachers%20also%20accused%20the%20local%20administration%2C%20which%20is%20run%20directly%20by%20the%20Centre%2C%20of%20%E2%80%9Cmuting%E2%80%9D%20the%20mention%20of%20Palestine%20in%20their%20sermons%20on%20Fridays%20at%20the%20mosques%20across%20the%20Valley.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDue%20to%20%E2%80%9Cverbal%20instructions%E2%80%9D%20by%20the%20authorities%20of%20J%26amp%3BK%20Wakf%20Board