p%20made-in-India%20surgical%20reports.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20case%20involved%20a%2022-year-old%20female%20diagnosed%20with%20an%20atrial%20septal%20defect%20%E2%80%94%20a%20congenital%20heart%20condition%20characterised%20by%20a%20hole%20in%20the%20septum%2C%20the%20wall%20that%20separates%20the%20heart%E2%80%99s%20upper%20chambers%20(atria).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20was%20diagnosed%20quite%20late%20and%20was%20in%20a%20critical%20condition.%20The%20hospital%20was%20charging%20Rs%204%20lakh%20for%20the%20surgery%2C%20and%20her%20brother%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20afford%20it.%20While%20the%20doctor%20volunteered%20to%20do%20it%20for%20free%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F263106%2Finspiring-ahmednagar-doctor-couple-free-rescue-homeless-destitute-women%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20hospital%20did%20not.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHis%20brother%20asked%20for%20some%20time%20and%20tried%20to%20raise%20the%20money%2C%20but%20unfortunately%2C%20I%20never%20heard%20from%20them%20again.%20To%20be%20honest%2C%20it%20still%20haunts%20me%2C%E2%80%9D%20Dr%20Sudhir%20recalls%20in%20a%20conversation%20with%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20incident%20left%20him%20with%20sleepless%20nights%20and%20a%20mission%20%E2%80%94%20to%20develop%20a%20cost-effective%20system%20that%20can%20help%20people%20from%20every%20background%20in%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20outcome%20was%20the%20creation%20of%20a%20surgical%20robot%20called%20SSI%20Mantra.%20This%20innovative%20technology%20assists%20doctors%20in%20conducting%20complex%20surgeries%20with%20precision%20and%20ease%2C%20reducing%20costs%20by%20one-third%20compared%20to%20manual%20surgeries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20science%20company%20with%20a%20mission%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBorn%20in%20Rajasthan%2C%20Dr%20Sudhir%20moved%20to%20the%20US%20in%201972%20for%20his%20postgraduate%20studies.%20He%20completed%20his%20residency%20in%20Cardiothoracic%20Surgery%20at%20the%20University%20of%20British%20Columbia%20in%20Vancouver%2C%20Canada.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20practised%20for%20some%20years%20in%20Texas%20before%20becoming%20the%20founding%20chairman%20of%20Alliance%20Hospital%2C%20a%20centre%20for%20cardiovascular%20disease%20in%20West%20Texas%2C%20along%20with%2010%20other%20physicians.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20556px)%20100vw%2C%20556px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FScreenshot-2023-11-21-200519-1700577350.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22556%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20surgical%20robot%20reduces%20risks%20in%20surgery%20and%20increases%20recovery%20rate.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FScreenshot-2023-11-21-200519-1700577350.jpg%20556w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FScreenshot-2023-11-21-200519-1700577350-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FScreenshot-2023-11-21-200519-1700577350-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FScreenshot-2023-11-21-200519-1700577350-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-334640%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22291%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20surgical%20robot%20reduces%20risks%20in%20surgery%20and%20increases%20the%20recovery%20rate%3B%20Picture%20credit%3A%20SSI%20Innovations%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20was%20always%20interested%20in%20minimally%20invasive%20approaches%20when%20it%20came%20to%20surgeries%20and%20not%20splitting%20open%20the%20sternum.%20This%20is%20where%20I%20got%20the%20chance%20to%20perform%20various%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F166057%2Findia-surgery-robot-innovation-gujarat-news%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erobotic%20surgeries%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%2030%20percent%20of%20the%20patients%20went%20home%20in%20a%20day%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20recalls.%20%E2%80%9CHaving%20performed%20so%20many%20robotic%20surgeries%2C%20I%20would%20come%20to%20India%20to%20train%20people%20in%20robotic%20surgeries.%20Back%20then%2C%20India%20did%20not%20have%20its%20own%20robotic%20system.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202002%2C%20he%20performed%20his%20first%20robotic%20surgery%20in%20India.%20%E2%80%9CI%20kept%20coming%20back%20to%20the%20country%20but%20in%202011%2C%20I%20got%20an%20offer%20from%20a%20major%20hospital%20to%20launch%20their%20robotic%20surgery%20programme%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Sudhir%20says%20he%20had%20always%20longed%20to%20be%20back%20home%2C%20so%20he%20jumped%20at%20the%20opportunity%2C%20packed%20his%20bags%2C%20and%20moved%20back%20with%20his%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAt%20that%20time%2C%20there%20were%20only%20six%20to%20seven%20robotic%20systems%2C%20that%20too%20exported%2C%20so%20there%20were%20not%20many%20patients%20that%20could%20afford%20to%20pay%20those%20two%20to%20three%20lakh%20rupees%20more%20for%20robotic%20surgery.%20It%20was%20around%20this%20time%20when%20I%20met%20the%2022-year-old%20patient%E2%80%99s%20brother%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20whole%20incident%20made%20the%20doctor%20realise%20that%20the%20country%20needs%20a%20system%20that%20is%20cheaper.%20%E2%80%9CBecause%20of%20the%20high%20costs%20we%20cannot%20offer%20the%20best%20treatment%20to%20the%20patients%2C%20and%20to%20reduce%20the%20cost%2C%20we%20have%20to%20develop%20it%20in%20the%20country%20itself%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20the%20doctor%20made%20a%20commitment%20to%20the%20cause%20and%20decided%20to%20put%20his%20practice%20on%20hold%20in%202013.%20%E2%80%9CHaving%20done%20over%201%2C400%20surgeries%20and%20with%20my%20knowledge%20of%20robotic%20surgeries%2C%20I%20decided%20to%20use%20my%20life%20savings%20of%204.5%20million%20dollars%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CInitially%2C%20I%20went%20to%20Germany%20to%20meet%20some%20of%20their%20scientists%20for%20an%20exchange%20of%20technology.%20However%2C%20it%20was%20not%20a%20success.%20Then%2C%20I%20came%20back%20to%20India%20and%20formed%20a%20team%20of%2010%20engineers%20and%20started%20the%20development%20out%20of%20my%20home%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhy%20robotic%20surgeries%20and%20how%20do%20they%20work%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Sudhir%20explains%20why%20robotic%20surgeries%20are%20important.%20%E2%80%9CDepth%2C%20precision%20and%20safety.%20These%20are%20three%20things%20that%20surmise%20why%20we%20need%20robotic%20surgeries.%20With%20the%20help%20of%20technology%2C%20the%20surgeon%20gets%20an%20in-depth%20picture%20of%20the%20patient%E2%80%99s%20parts%20to%20be%20operated%20on%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20informs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Frobot-4-1700577778.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20technology%20has%20successfully%20assisted%20doctors%20in%20performing%20500%20surgeries%20so%20far%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Frobot-4-1700577778.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Frobot-4-1700577778-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Frobot-4-1700577778-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Frobot-4-1700577778-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Frobot-4-1700577778-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-334641%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20technology%20has%20successfully%20performed%20500%20surgeries%20so%20far%3B%20Picture%20credit%3A%20SSI%20Innovations%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20high-end%20images%20make%20the%20surgery%20more%20precise%20and%20hence%20safer.%20The%20surgeon%20would%20have%20to%20worry%20to%20be%20accurate%20with%20something%20as%20simple%20yet%20risky%20as%20stitching%20a%20wound%20with%20a%20beating%20heart%20underneath%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20doctor%20initially%20developed%20SSI%20Mantra%2C%20but%20after%20a%20while%2C%20he%20launched%20an%20enhanced%20version%20called%20SSI%20Mantra%202.%20The%20goal%20of%20the%20system%20was%20to%20make%20it%20user-friendly%2C%20ergonomic%2C%20and%20with%20more%20features%20%E2%80%94%20both%20for%20the%20surgeons%20as%20well%20as%20for%20the%20table-side%20assisting%20team.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhat%20we%20have%20designed%20is%20called%20an%20open-face%20console%2C%20featuring%20a%20large%2032-inch%204K%20high-definition%20resolution%203D%20monitor.%20This%20design%20enhances%20magnification%2C%20providing%20surgeons%20with%20the%20capability%20to%20perform%20procedures%20with%20exceptional%20precision.%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20remarkable%20advancement%20for%20surgical%20procedures%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20he%20says%20they%20have%20integrated%20safety%20features%20with%20a%20head-tracking%20camera.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20surgeon%20wears%20glasses%20with%20specific%20markers%20that%20are%20tracked%20by%20the%20camera.%20This%20ensures%20that%20if%20the%20surgeon%20looks%20away%20from%20the%20monitor%2C%20even%20while%20moving%20their%20hands%2C%20the%20system%20will%20not%20respond.%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20safety%20measure%20that%20requires%20the